hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"同好WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年同中學呀SIR捉第一步咁行俾佢屌我冇章法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"有章法好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都用一模一樣既模式仲捉咩棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"正規的係要背譜<br />\n台灣的象棋軟件係列埋常有行法<br />\n勝負和率幾多<br />\n<br />\n所以話現今的象棋學習<br />\n差人幾條街"}]}